<h1>Equality Engine</h1>
<h2>About</h2>
<p>The equality engine is an open source implementation of the equality system, a resource based socio-economic system designed to ensure a fair and equal distribution of rights, privileges, and benefits to all members.</p>
<h2>Status</h2>
<p>The Equality Engine is still in early alpha development.</p>
<h2>Roadmap</h2>
<p>The following items are on the current roadmap</p>
<ul>
<li>Voting - including unique tokens for each vote to make it more difficult to obtain a voters identity by compromising a table containing votes</li>
<li>A city database</li>
<li>A database structure that defines business templates including what resources a business needs to operate - including scaling factors</li>
<li>Database encryption of all personal information fields</li>
</ul>
